"title": "2203: Jesus Christ, titles and names of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2203",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>These, in their rich variety, throw light on either the person of Jesus Christ or on some aspect of his ministry.</p>\n<h2>Titles relating to Jesus Christ's identity</h2>\n<h3>The exact image of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>The first and last, the Alpha and Omega</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:13\">REV 22:13</a></strong> <em>“Alpha” and “Omega” are the first and last letters of the Greek alphabet.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17\">REV 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:8\">REV 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:6\">REV 21:6</a></p>\n<h3>The Word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1\">JHN 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1\">MAL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:13\">REV 19:13</a></p>\n<h3>The last Adam</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45\">1CO 15:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:14\">ROM 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>The bright Morning Star</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>The rising sun</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:2\">MAL 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:78\">LUK 1:78</a></p>\n<h3>The Living One</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:18\">REV 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:26\">JHN 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25\">JHN 11:25</a></p>\n<h3>The Amen</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20\">2CO 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>The true light</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3-John1:9\">JHN 1:3–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2\">ISA 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:32\">LUK 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:21\">JHN 3:19–3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:46\">JHN 12:46</a></p>\n<h3>The Righteous One</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:14\">ACT 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:6\">JER 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15-Jer33:16\">JER 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:52\">ACT 7:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14\">ACT 22:14</a></p>\n<h3>The Lion of Judah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>The king of the Jews</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:1-Matt2:2\">MAT 2:1–2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:37\">MAT 27:37</a></p>\n<h2>The ``I am'' sayings of John's Gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:58\">JHN 8:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35\">JHN 6:35</a> <em>the bread of life</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:5\">JHN 9:5</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:7-John10:10\">JHN 10:7–10:10</a> <em>the gate</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11-John10:14\">JHN 10:11–10:14</a> <em>the good shepherd</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25\">JHN 11:25</a> <em>the resurrection and the life</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a> <em>the way, the truth and the life</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:1-John15:5\">JHN 15:1–15:5</a> <em>the true vine</em></p>\n<h2>Titles relating to Jesus Christ's ministry</h2>\n<h3>The seed of Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:16\">GAL 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:7\">GEN 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:15\">GEN 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:7\">GEN 24:7</a></p>\n<h3>The Root and Offspring of David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The faithful witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:4\">ISA 55:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:37\">JHN 18:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Immanuel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:23\">MAT 1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:14\">ISA 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:8\">ISA 8:8</a></p>\n<h3>The capstone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:20-Eph2:21\">EPH 2:20–2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:6–2:7</a></p>\n<h3>The rock</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:4\">1CO 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:32-Rom9:33\">ROM 9:32–9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>The bridegroom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:29\">JHN 3:29</a></strong> <em>John the Baptist describing himself as the bridegroom's friend, and Jesus Christ as the bridegroom.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:15\">MAT 9:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:19-Mark2:20\">MRK 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:34-Luke5:35\">LUK 5:34–5:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:1-Matt25:10\">MAT 25:1–25:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h3>The firstborn among many brothers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a></p>\n<h3>The firstfruits</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:23\">1CO 15:23</a></p>\n<h3>The firstborn from the dead</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>The heir of all things</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>Titles relating to Jesus Christ's authority</h2>\n<h3>Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:25\">ACT 2:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:46\">LUK 6:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:68\">JHN 6:68</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13\">ROM 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:5\">1CO 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:23\">COL 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>The head of the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22-Eph1:23\">EPH 1:22–1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23\">EPH 5:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">COL 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>The Chief Shepherd</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:6\">MAT 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:25\">1PE 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20\">HEB 13:20</a></p>\n<h3>Prince</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a></p>\n<h3>Rabbi</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:38\">JHN 1:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:16\">JHN 20:16</a></p>\n<h2>Titles emphasising Jesus Christ's saving work</h2>\n<h3>Jesus: the LORD saves</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Man of sorrows</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a></p>\n<h3>The Passover lamb</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:7\">1CO 5:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>A horn of salvation</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69\">LUK 1:69</a></p>\n<h3>The consolation of Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:68\">LUK 1:68</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25\">LUK 2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:38\">LUK 2:38</a></p>\n<h3>The deliverer and Redeemer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:26\">ROM 11:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:20\">ISA 59:20</a></p>\n<h3>The author and perfecter of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Titles stressing Jesus Christ's mediatory status</h2>\n<h3>The Mediator</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1TI 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>The high priest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">HEB 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:20\">HEB 6:20</a></p>\n<h3>The Son of Man</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:19\">MAT 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:24\">LUK 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:13\">JHN 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:53\">JHN 6:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:56\">ACT 7:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13\">REV 1:13</a></p>",
